    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine. This unit exhibits exceptional mechanical integrity, with a documented Vanos system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement already completed to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The naturally aspirated powerplant delivers a visceral 8,000 RPM redline through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a recent comprehensive bushing refresh and Bilstein suspension components. This is a true turn-key enthusiast's example with flawless paint depth and a pristine, original interior. No deferred maintenance; just pure, unadulterated driving dynamics.",
